snippet.title: Fistful of Nothing  - HUMBLE TROVE Trailer
snippet.description:
You are stuck in a building with no exit, Surrounded by armed gunmen and elevators that choose to not work properly. Use an empty gun and your wits to trick your way to safety to LIVE to see another day!

- Design & Code -
Salman Shurie (@Salman_Shh)

- Music & SFX -
Britt Brady (@Britt_t_Brady)

- Development & Art -
Andre Steen (@drestuff)

- Check out the game on Humble Trove
https://www.humblebundle.com/subscription/trove
